rows.label: qst104503_msg001
rows.name: LIST_QST104503の仮イベント

rows.label: qst104503_msg0001
rows.name:
Good job friends! Everyone
make it across safely!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0002
rows.name:
Now is time to start selling
stuffs to Superbian milita...

rows.label: qst104503_msg0003
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... Sniff-sniff...
Uh-oh. This not good.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0004
rows.name:
Kukuso smell same scent as products
we brought coming from all around!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0005
rows.name:
Are products that we bring already
supplied as standard by military?!
We not sell anything at this rate!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0006
rows.name:
Mo-mo... Mo-mo-mo... Kukuso
know! Must get new product
lineup here in Temperantia!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0007
rows.name:
Collect things that seem
useful from around here,
and make into product!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0008
rows.name:
Friends very kind. Kukuso
maybe start crying...

rows.label: qst104503_msg0009
rows.name:
Okay. Please find Kukuso any useful
materials from Temperantia!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0010
rows.name:
Just need enough materials to
be able to start up business!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0011
rows.name: Kukuso will be waiting then!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0101
rows.name:
Friends bring Kukuso useful
Temperantia materials?

rows.label: qst104503_msg0102
rows.name:
Still needing more materials to start
up shop! Kukuso wait right here!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0201
rows.name:
Please bring Metal Brooch for Kukuso.
Very popular item with soldiers.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0202
rows.name:
Kukuso just need 10 in total.
Good luck with searching!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0301
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... Sniff-sniff...
Is that smell of rare treasure
Kukuso can only sell here?!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0302
rows.name:
Ah, Metal Brooches! Kukuso still
not sure why these so valuable.

rows.label: qst104503_msg0303
rows.name:
But if soldiers have demand
for them, is job of Nopon
to provide supply!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0304
rows.name:
Now Kukuso have perfect lineup
for initial shop opening!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0305
rows.name:
By the way, where friends
find those brooches?

rows.label: qst104503_msg0306
rows.name: At coast just nearby? Thanks for info!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0307
rows.name:
No need for worry. Kukuso collect
treasure using most covert sneaking
techniques! Monsters never know!

rows.label: qst104503_msg0308
rows.name:
Thanks, friends, for all of helping!
Please take this as thanks!
